 <title>Circuito Arte.mov - RJ</title>
 <link>http://ubalab.org/blog/circuito-artemov-rj</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Amanhã de manhã rumo ao Rio de Janeiro, onde vou participar do Circuito Arte.mov (flyer abaixo).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Circuito Arte.mov - Filipeta&quot; src=&quot;/sites/ubalab.org/files/images/CAM_filipeta_web_4_45JJ.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No fim de semana vamos em caravana para a &lt;a href=&quot;http://nuvem.tk/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Nuvem&lt;/a&gt;, em Mauá, pra trabalhar com &lt;a href=&quot;http://nuvem.tk/wiki/index.php/Cartografias_Experimentais&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Cartografias Experimentais&lt;/a&gt; e uma &lt;a href=&quot;http://nuvem.tk/noticias&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Oficina de Mapeamento Aéreo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Nuvem - Mapeamento Aéreo&quot; src=&quot;http://nuvem.tk/?noticias.head.132931344541&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-1 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/mapas&quot;&gt;mapas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/geo&quot;&gt;geo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/rio&quot;&gt;rio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/nuvem&quot;&gt;nuvem&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/maua&quot;&gt;mauá&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tag/artemov&quot;&gt;artemov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
